<item>
            <title>[LU-3826] copytool restore should set owner of volatile file before copy</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-3826</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;HSM restore fails for files not owned by root since the copytool does not set the ownership of the volatile file and layout swap required that the two files have the same ownership.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="20566">LU-3826</key>
            <summary>copytool restore should set owner of volatile file before copy</summary>
                <type id="1" iconUrl="https://jira.whamcloud.com/secure/viewavatar?size=xsmall&amp;avatarId=11303&amp;avatarType=issuetype">Bug</type>
